6,'mfn-page-items-seo','<img src=\"http://myshikshak.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/creative2.png\" alt=\"\"/>\n\n<h1  style=\"color:#ADFF2F;font-size:60px \"><b><u>KNOW YOUR SELF 2K17</u></b></h1>\n\n<h3><b>KNOW YOURSELF 2K17</b> is an exam that offers a real test of Mental ability and presence of mind for school students, this test is a big platform to avail Scholarship, Cash prizes, Career counselling and many different benefits and reward. \r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<b>KNOW YOURSELF 2K17</b> is organized by <a href=\"http://myshikshak.com\"><b style=\"color:#0000ff \">MYSHIKSHAK.COM</b></a> which is a leading pinnacle in education sector in Meerut. <b>KNOW YOURSELF 2K17</b> is an exam at city level that will offer a real test to know students mental presence in their respective age group on such a big platform. Over 10,000 thousand students, including best schools across the city are expected to register for the exam this year to put their skills against each other.\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<b>KNOW YOURSELF 2K17</b> is a first of its kind exam which will be conduct across 50 centers in <b>MEERUT</b>. More than <b>10,000 students</b> are going to register for the exam from the 6th to 12th standard of senior secondary school across different streams of education including all state board, central board and ICSE.\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nThe exam is going to held in 3 groups on the basis of class.\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<b> Group A  for (6th to 8th) - Champ\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n Group B  for (9th to 10th) - Junior\r\n<br>\r\n<br> \r\nGroup C  for (11th to 12th) - Senior</b>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nRegistrations for <b>KNOW YOURSELF 2K17</b>  can be done by submitting the form on the given link <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2jomFHv\"><b style=\"color:#0000ff \">Registration Link</b></a>  on behalf of  school management.\r\n\r\n<br> \r\n<br>\r\n       \r\n Please note that there is <b>Only ₹ 50 Registration</b> Fee per student participant for the exam.\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nThe format and syllabus of the exam is designed on the basis of common general knowledge and reasoning and based on general logic\'s and smart approach and thinking capacity that the students are expected to appear in near future for their further academic & career pursuit.\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n \r\nBenefits to Students:-\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<b>Financial Scholarships (as tuition fee of next year) for Top 3 student.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCash prizes, fee exemption and exciting goodies to Top 10 students.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMedals and Excellence certificates for Top 50 Students.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMerit Certificates for Top 100 students in each groups. \r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nParticipation Certificates to all the qualified students.\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMerit students will get discount in fee on enrolling themselves in preparation of various competitive exams.</b>   \r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<b>Life time FREE counselling</b> support by the <a href=\"http://myshikshak.com\"><b style=\"color:#0000ff \">MY SHIKSHAK</b></a> team to all the student .\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br> \r\n\r\nThis exam will help students to take admission in various prestigious institute of state.\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nFor more details you can also visit the <a href=\"http://myshikshak.com\"><b style=\"color:#0000ff \">MY SHIKSHAK</b></a> website <a href=\"http://myshikshak.com\"><b style=\"color:#0000ff \">www.myshikshak.com</b> </a>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\nIn view of this excellent opportunity for the students to showcase their mental strength and knowledge among their groups and avail thousand of benefits by <a href=\"http://myshikshak.com\"><b style=\"color:#0000ff \">www.myshikshak.com</b></a>.\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>  \r\n\r\nI request you to please share this piece of information with your school students & other eligible participants currently studying in  6th to 12th  standard  of your school.</h3>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\n\njustify\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\n'),(292