m/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/tutor.png4_.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n<h4> <ul>\r\n<li>We will provide you the platform to showcase your talent & enhance your skills.</li>\r\n<li>We take care of your better learning along with professional advancement.</li>\r\n<li>We will provide you all the possible necessities for your development and growth.</li>\r\n</ul></h4>\r\n\r\n<h3><img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://myshikshak.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/teamwork_icon_team_work_success_business_corporate_people_hands_management_organization-512-e1470959317661.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<b style=\"color:#ff5733\">For Parents/Students</b></h3>\r\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://myshikshak.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/3-1.png\" alt=\"\" />\r\n\r\n<h4><ul>\r\n<li>We apply all the best possible learning strategies which helps in overall development of students.</li>\r\n<li>We will provide education with the best quality along with the most catchy, interesting & strategical way.</li>\r\n<li>We assured grooming of your child in various fields such as Dance, Music, Sports, Technology, Social Work & many more...</li>\r\n</ul></h4>\r\n<br>\n\njustify\n\n#ffffff\n\nrepeat;left top;;\n\nbounceIn\n\nHow We Work\n\n<br>\r\n<img class=\"scale-with-grid\" src=\"http://myshikshak.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Collages1.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n<br>\n\njustify\n\n#ffffff\n\nrepeat;right top;;\n\nbounceInLeft\n\ncircle up\n\n#ff5733\n\n'),(1740,2367,'mfn-post-layout','no-sidebar'),(1741,2501,'_wp_attached_file','2016/08/Collages1.jpg'),(1742,2501,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:3072;s:6:\"height\";i:5120;s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"2016/08/Collages1.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:15:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"Collages1-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"Collages1-180x300.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:180;s:6:\"height\";i:300;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:12:\"medi